structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 17, sec. 52, effective January 1, 1978. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 84. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 193, secs. 1 and 2. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 136d-1, 136d-2.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Stenographer in counties containing a city of the third, fourth, or fifth class or 50,000 or more population.
